subject: Re: New QuikScript font: QuikScript Geometric
msgSnippet: This is nice. I completely agree with everything said about the venerable Kingsley. I ve actually been working on some new Quikscript fonts of my own, but
messageBody:
This is nice. I completely agree with everything said about the venerable Kingsley.
I've actually been working on some new Quikscript fonts of my own, but they're not ready for release yet (I'm a complete novice at making fonts).
